    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Cast Outs》让魔法的视觉冲击拉满，让你在施法时同时感受到力量和爽快！加入这个奇幻的都市战场，无论技术高低，你和你的好友都能通力协作，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受这场快节奏，超高能的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/52496a6e16074de03b1d209b19afdf56.poster.avif?t=1772197296\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/52496a6e16074de03b1d209b19afdf56.webm?t=1772197296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/52496a6e16074de03b1d209b19afdf56.mp4?t=1772197296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >施法如同重拳，爆发如同开炮。在冲击力实足的魔法战场上，你就是决定胜负的关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/4053e6783575fb820c32a281ae3dd750.poster.avif?t=1772197296\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/4053e6783575fb820c32a281ae3dd750.webm?t=1772197296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/4053e6783575fb820c32a281ae3dd750.mp4?t=1772197296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >咒语组合，威力无穷！和你的小队一起，探索并驾驭多种魔法组合技，激发无限潜能！单打独斗，你很强。团队出击？你无敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/e1a6a45763cc87fe831c50c7eaa0bbf2.poster.avif?t=1772197296\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/e1a6a45763cc87fe831c50c7eaa0bbf2.webm?t=1772197296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/e1a6a45763cc87fe831c50c7eaa0bbf2.mp4?t=1772197296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻度 Rogue 元素让每局都是全新体验。Mutator 可以改变技能、升级能力、解锁新组合，让每一战都不可预测。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/3509bc4d3fbb792df76b8e362f113a75.poster.avif?t=1772197296\" width=1170 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/3509bc4d3fbb792df76b8e362f113a75.webm?t=1772197296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/3509bc4d3fbb792df76b8e362f113a75.mp4?t=1772197296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兽人、食人魔、独眼巨人、幽灵、巨龙……敌人如潮水般涌入伦敦。这里是你的家园，如今却沦为战场，你必须将它夺回！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种英雄，多样玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >交替使用不同英雄，探索多种玩法和组合技。快去实战中尝试、组合、发现全新的团队策略吧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高能不停，随时开战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 分钟不过瘾，玩上通宵不停歇。《Cast Outs》拒绝刷取，提供高能迭起的爽快体验，让战斗停不下来。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样玩法，随时合作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论两人、三人或四人小队，你们的目的都是联手保卫城市！战斗冒险、护送任务、生存模式、速通和挑战模式，拯救城市就看你们的了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras/ad54b951a3a8298e7dc9893d490b1717.avif?t=1772197296\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307340/extras_big/ad54b951a3a8298e7dc9893d490b1717.avif?t=1772197296 width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">每场战斗都是为了合作，也为了朋友。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">但更为了那些任务结束后还会津津乐道的回忆。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>",
